      "value": "<p>Cost: 2 Creation Points </p><p>CCD Drain: 5 Chakra || Bulk: 2 </p><p></p><p>Effect: When you select this perk, you fit your medallion with a yellow fluid that smells of bananas.</p><p> While not in difficult terrain, increase your movement speed by +10 feet.</p><p> You may also Dash or Disengage as a bonus action, and ignore the first rank of Exhaustion.</p><p> Once per round, on your turn you may spend 10 chakra from your CCD to gain the benefits of the Dash or Disengage action (no action required).</p><p></p>",
